<p>Update on Focus</p><p>Hello everyone and sorry for the lack of contact recently, this was because I had become disillusioned as I said in my last post.</p><p>The lack of focus issue is now an even bigger problem and I am struggling to function at work. This may be because my life situation is pretty hopeless from a work and business point of view. I am able to operate perfectly well in other areas, for instance creative pursuits, reading, looking after my family I can do with no problem. It is just work.</p><p>Any ideas on how to regain focus would be most welcome</p>
